OL,3,CPrince William urges men to talk about
OL,4,Cmental health as he opens new centre
OL,6,FThe Prince of Wales has urged more men
OL,7,Fto talk about their mental health as
OL,8,Fhe opened a new centre in Birmingham,
OL,9,Fworking to help prevent male suicides.
OL,11,FPrince William officially opened
OL,12,FJames' Place Birmingham, in Edgbaston,
OL,13,Fwhich is designed to offer "rapid,
OL,14,Fprofessional therapy to men that
OL,15,Faddresses the root causes of suicidal
OL,16,Fcrisis".
OL,18,FSpeaking at the centre today (Monday
OL,19,F11 May), the Prince said he hoped the
OL,20,Fcharity would be able to open more
OL,21,Ffacilities around the country.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778620286
OL,3,CPrince William urges men to talk about
OL,4,Cmental health as he opens new centre
OL,6,FThe Prince has previously opened the
OL,7,Fcharity's centres in Liverpool, London
OL,8,Fand Newcastle.
OL,10,FHe said: "The team here are fantastic.
OL,12,F"I hope we can get more of you around
OL,13,Fthe UK, because it is in need of it
OL,14,Fsadly.
OL,16,F"We need to talk more about suicide,
OL,17,Ftalk more about preventing it and talk
OL,18,Fabout getting it to young men and
OL,19,Fwomen earlier, so we don't have to
OL,20,Fhave these centres in the very long
OL,21,Frun.
OL,26,@rD@JOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778620286
OL,3,CPrince William urges men to talk about
OL,4,Cmental health as he opens new centre
OL,6,F"That is the aim."
OL,8,FThe charity was founded by the parents
OL,9,Fof James Wentworth-Stanley, aged 21,
OL,10,Fwho took his own life nearly 20 years
OL,11,Fago.
OL,13,FJames died 10 days after a minor
OL,14,Foperation, having been unable to
OL,15,Faccess the urgent support he needed
OL,16,Ffor severe anxiety and suicidal
OL,17,Fthoughts.
OL,19,FHis parents wanted to help prevent
OL,20,Fother families from losing the men
OL,21,Fthey love.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778620286
OL,3,CPrince William urges men to talk about
OL,4,Cmental health as he opens new centre
OL,6,FFormer service-user Ben Brand, who
OL,7,Ftravelled from Bedford for the
OL,8,FPrince's visit, said: "It allows
OL,9,Fpeople to get access to the help they
OL,10,Fneed very, very quickly.
OL,12,F"From my experience, it was less than
OL,13,F48 hours before sending a referral in
OL,14,Fand being in crisis to actually being
OL,15,Fsat in front of therapist. I then
OL,16,Fsubsequently had eight sessions after
OL,17,Fthat, every week.
OL,26,@pD@WOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778620286
OL,3,CPrince William urges men to talk about
OL,4,Cmental health as he opens new centre
OL,6,F"You couldn't get that service
OL,7,Felsewhere and as far as I'm aware,
OL,8,Fit's the only place that could get you
OL,9,Fthat quality of care that quickly,
OL,10,Fwhich is just vital, crucial, really.
OL,12,F"There's a massive need for it, and
OL,13,Fbeing able to get people in the door
OL,14,Fthat quickly, and get them help that
OL,15,Fquickly ` that is the life-saving
OL,16,Fpart."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778620286
OL,3,CPrince William urges men to talk about
OL,4,Cmental health as he opens new centre
OL,6,FMarcus Davies, another former service-
OL,7,Fuser and a trustee at the charity,
OL,8,Fadded: "It was rapid, it gave me what
OL,9,FI needed when I needed it. I didn't
OL,10,Fhave to wait on a waiting list.
OL,12,F"I'm confident enough to say that I
OL,13,Fwouldn't be here had I not had the
OL,14,Fintervention when I had it."
OL,16,FMr Davies said the Prince of Wales'
OL,17,Fvisit could help inform more men in
OL,18,Fcrisis about the charity.
OL,26,@pD@HOUtD@AOUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778620286
OL,3,CPrince William urges men to talk about
OL,4,Cmental health as he opens new centre
OL,6,FHe said: "I think for that publicity,
OL,7,Fhis reach and the audience that he can
OL,8,Freach through his status and who he
OL,9,Fis, I think that's just critical to
OL,10,Fgetting that message far and wide.
OL,12,F"I had never heard of James's Place
OL,13,Fprior to my GP referring me. It's so
OL,14,Fimportant that men know that it is
OL,15,Fthere and available as a service to
OL,16,Fhelp those that need it.
OL,18,F"The more far and wide that message
OL,19,Fcan be delivered, the better ` and he
OL,20,Fhas the scope to be able to do that."
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@AOUzD@AOU|D@eO]
